        "created_at": "2025-09-25T17:25:34.241Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Signal prompted me to update, but after installing it never reopened. When I tried to reopen it, it said sorry not supported and put the cross over the app icon.</p>\n<p>The app should not permit this to have happened in the first place, but regardless.</p>\n<p>I can’t find any option on your website to download an older version, and I’m not in the habit of downloading new OS updates unless I have to because they always break something.</p>",
