        "created_at": "2025-09-26T05:54:50.015Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I think it will still expire in 90 days though, so you may need to update your OS before. Of course it’s always best to keep Signal up to date to be able to use latest features/security updates, but it’s a quick solution for now</p>",
