        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/aihpcfl/{size}/3917_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-09-26T12:06:13.068Z",
        "cooked": "<p>To add to <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/contributor\">@Contributor</a> there is another reason to keep Signal updated.  I had a case where a contact could not open a PDF I sent him.  It turned out he had not updated Signal in a while.  He updated and found he could then open the PDF.  In general, there may be other potential issues like this if you don’t keep updated.  Just FYI.</p>",
