        "id": 276102,
        "name": "Billybob",
        "username": "blabeob",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/b/ac8455/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-09-26T14:21:09.580Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The issue is not updating signal, the issue is requiring an entire OS update as well.</p>\n<p>Say I update signal to fix issues with sending PDFs, but the OS update I have to install breaks something in my other software that I use daily. So at this point I have to upgrade to an entirely new OS etc etc</p>\n<p>I have a lot of software that costs money to get a new license for every time I install an entirely new macOS. I grow tired from the endless march of software updates that costs money to fix every time.</p>\n<p>Thank you for your help.</p>",
